      • PlannerProcess

        public PlannerProcess(DialogueState initState)
        Creates the planning process. Timeout is set to twice the maximum sampling time. Then, runs the planner until the horizon has been reached, or the planner has run out of time. Adds the best action to the dialogue state.
        Parameters:
        initState - initial dialogue state.
